<h1 style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: small;">BYU-Idaho Worker's Compensation Claim Form</span></h1>
<h2 style="text-align: center;">For Full and Part Time Employees</h2>
<h4 style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: x-small;">Please fill in all fields as much as possible.</span></h4>
<p style="text-align: center;"><span style="text-align: center; color: #ff0000;">(All yellow fields are required.)</span></p>
<hr />
<p class="center">NOTICE:</p>
<ul>
