<li><span style="color: #000000; font-size: small;">REPORT MINOR INJURIES WITHIN 24 HOURS. </span></li>
<li><span style="color: #000000; font-size: small;">FAILURE TO COMPLETE ALL SECTIONS OF THIS FORM MAY DELAY CLAIM AND/OR PAYMENT OF BENEFITS. </span></li>
</ul>
